'''氣候緊急狀態宣言'''是一項由各地[[政府|政府]]以及[[科學家|科學家]]發起的行動，宣告[[人類|人類]]已進入{{tsl|en|Climate crisis|氣候危機|氣候緊急狀態}}（Climate Emergency），須立即採取行動遏止[[氣候變化|氣候變化]]，以避免潛在和不可逆轉的[[環境破壞|環境破壞]]發生<ref name="綠色生活21天">{{cite web |title=我宣告，為氣候改變 - 綠色生活21 天 - 綠藤生機 |url=https://21daysofgreen.greenvines.com.tw/climate-emergency/index.html |website=綠色生活21 天 |access-date=2020-12-08 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925073248/https://21daysofgreen.greenvines.com.tw/climate-emergency/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=綠色和平氣候與能源專案小組 |title=上萬名科學家連署 氣候緊急宣言為地球拉警報 |url=https://www.greenpeace.org/taiwan/update/11832/ |work=綠色和平 |date=2019-12-23 |accessdate=2020-12-08 |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021101517/https://www.greenpeace.org/taiwan/update/11832/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該宣言於2016年12月在[[澳洲|澳洲]]{{tsl|en|City of Darebin|德爾賓市}}首次發起<ref>{{cite web |title=History of Local Government Declarations |url=https://www.caceonline.org/history.html |website=CACE |publisher=Council and Community Action in the Climate Emergency |accessdate=2020-01-06 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030013345/https://www.caceonline.org/history.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{as of|2020|12}}，33 個國家的共1,800個[[地方政府|地方政府]]一同響應了這項宣言<ref>{{cite web |title=CEDAMIA list of global declarations |url=https://www.cedamia.org/global/ |website=CEDAMIA |publisher=Climate Emergency Declaration and Mobilisation In Action |accessdate=2020-02-23 |archive-date=2020-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204051940/https://www.cedamia.org/global/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

簽署「氣候緊急狀態宣言」，代表政府承認[[氣候變遷|氣候變遷]]（[[全球暖化|全球暖化]]效應）的存在，而現有措施遠不足以應對現今的情況，需要改變。宣佈世界進入氣候緊急狀態，更代表過去的[[防災|防災]]體系規劃，面對氣候極端變化，已變得脆弱且逐漸失效，需要提出更為緊急的因應對策，積極正視未來的[[極端天氣|極端天氣]]事件及其各項[[災害|災害]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=2020台灣進入氣候緊急狀態 |url=https://udn.com/news/story/7339/4262494 |accessdate=2020-12-14 |date=2020-01-01 |work=聯合新聞 |language=zh-hant |author1=彭啟明 |archive-date=2020-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200102132231/https://udn.com/news/story/7339/4262494 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Gorey |first1=Colm |title=What Does Declaring a Climate Emergency Actually Mean? |url=https://www.siliconrepublic.com/innovation/climate-emergency-ireland-what-it-means |accessdate=2019-12-12 |publisher=Silicon Republic |date=2019-05-10 |archive-date=2019-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212200420/https://www.siliconrepublic.com/innovation/climate-emergency-ireland-what-it-means |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Resolution |first1=Climate Emergency |title=What is a Climate Emergency Declaration |url=https://www.theclimatemobilization.org/climate-emergency-resolution |website=The Climate Mobilization |publisher=The Climate Mobilization |accessdate=2019-12-12 |archive-date=2019-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190627144916/https://www.theclimatemobilization.org/climate-emergency-resolution |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年12月12日，[[聯合國秘書長|聯合國秘書長]][[安東尼歐·古特瑞斯|-{zh-hans:安东尼奥·古特雷斯; zh-tw:安東尼歐·古特瑞斯; zh-mo:古德禮; zh-hant:安東尼奧·古特雷斯}-]]在《[[巴黎協定|巴黎協定]]》5週年-{zh-cn:视频; zh-tw:視訊; zh-hk:視像}-會議上呼籲各國宣布進入「氣候緊急狀態」<ref>{{Cite web |title=巴黎協定5週年 聯合國籲各國宣布氣候緊急狀態 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202012130097.aspx |accessdate=2020-12-13 |author=李佩珊 |date=2020-12-12 |publisher=中央通訊社 |language=zh-hant |editor=蔡佳敏 |location=布魯塞爾 |archive-date=2020-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213092450/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202012130097.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

